      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOTSHOT LILY (7) comes here after a scorching NG win at Richmond Straight over 324m in 17.52. In form and can measure up again. LAYTON MAGIC (5) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 25.15 beating Despicable Kyro. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Can measure up again. LATEST TWIST (1) has a strong record this trip with four wins and five placings from 12 starts. Below best last time at Gosford (30.10) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length sixth. Looks well placed here and among the chances. CRITICAL MOMENT (6) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a one length second (22.28) in a Grade 5 at Bulli. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from the tricky draw.",
